The command for precalculating the raw sequences is (replace path_to_blast_database with your local path):

$ get_raw_sequences -d /path/to/your/blast/db/nr/nr -o data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.xml.raw_seq data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.xml

The commands used to generate this output are:

$ genevalidator -x data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.xml data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.fasta -r data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.xml.raw_seq
or
$ genevalidator -x data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.tab data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.fasta -t "qseqid sseqid sacc slen qstart qend sstart send length qframe pident evalue" -r data/all_validations_prot/all_validations_prot_less.xml.raw_seq
